22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20(L)%20and%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20(R)%20were%20both%20at%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20conference%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Apple%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20OpenAI%20on%20Friday.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20OpenAI%20on%20Friday%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20stealing%20trade%20secrets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20iPhone%20maker%20accused%20OpenAI%20of%20poaching%20its%20engineers%20and%20accessing%20confidential%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20and%20business%20world%20weighed%20in%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-accuses-openai-of-playing-dirty-in-the-ai-talent-wars-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20talent%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20now%20be%20worthy%20of%20a%20Hollywood%20adaptation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20lawsuit%20that%20reads%20like%20a%20corporate%20crime%20thriller%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-sues-openai-trade-secret-theft-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20accused%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20poaching%20former%20Apple%20employees%2C%20conducting%20%26quot%3Bshow%20and%20tell%26quot%3B%20interviews%2C%20and%20accessing%20confidential%20documents%20to%20accelerate%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-new-device-screen-addiction-jony-ive-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsumer%20hardware%20push%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20centers%20on%20OpenAI's%20hiring%20of%20an%20Apple%20employee%20who%20Apple%20says%20kept%20a%20company%20laptop%2C%20exploited%20a%20security%20bug%20to%20access%20internal%20systems%20after%20leaving%2C%20downloaded%20confidential%20files%2C%20and%20helped%20others%20leaving%20for%20OpenAI%20to%20evade%20Apple's%20exit%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20says%20OpenAI%20asked%20candidates%20to%20bring%20physical%20components%20to%20interviews%20and%20used%20a%20shared%20supplier%20to%20replicate%20a%20proprietary%20Apple%20metal-finishing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20brief%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20secrets%20of%20other%20companies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20focused%20on%20building%20innovative%20technology%20that%20empowers%20people%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bombshell%20lawsuit%20between%20two%20of%20the%20premier%20tech%20companies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20which%20were%20once%20partners%2C%20has%20generated%20a%20lot%20of%20reaction.%20Here's%20what%20smart%20people%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20latest%20legal%20battle%20in%20Big%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d141e614-d066-4bea-8d56-7abbcb7e2c38%5C%22%3EJean%20Gan%2C%20AI%20governance%20leader%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJean%20Gan%2C%20director%20of%20legal%2C%20compliance%2C%20and%20enterprise%20risk%20at%20Savills%20Singapore%20Group%20and%20a%20Ph.D.%20researcher%20focused%20on%20AI%20and%20law%2C%20said%20that%20protecting%20trade%20secrets%2C%20particularly%20in%20California%2C%20is%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20how%20Apple%20pleaded%20this.%20California%20courts%20have%20largely%20rejected%20the%20inevitable%20disclosure%20doctrine%2C%20and%20the%20state%20won't%20enforce%20non-competes%2C%20so%20Apple%20can%20do%20nothing%20about%20the%20400%20former%20employees%20now%20at%20OpenAI%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BSo%20every%20allegation%20rests%20on%20conduct%3A%20retained%20devices%2C%20unauthorized%20access%2C%20misused%20documents%2C%20coached%20evasion.%20In%20a%20jurisdiction%20where%20talent%20moves%20freely%20by%20design%2C%20trade%20secrets%20law%20is%20the%20only%20legal%20perimeter%20left%20around%20institutional%20knowledge%2C%20and%20Apple%20has%20pleaded%20squarely%20inside%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20complaint%20highlights%20a%20serious%20risk%20to%20company%20secrets%3A%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20alleges%20OpenAI%20had%20a%20manufacturing%20partner%20perform%20a%20proprietary%20Apple%20metal-finishing%20technique%20and%20misled%20that%20partner%20into%20believing%20Apple%20had%20consented.%20That%20leak%20ran%20through%20a%20shared%20supplier.%20No%20employee%20needed%20to%20carry%20anything%20out%20the%20door.%20Supply%20chains%20move%20trade%20secrets%20just%20as%20easily%20as%20departing%20staff%20do%2C%20and%20few%20confidentiality%20frameworks%20treat%20them%20with%20the%20same%20rigor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad0cb333-480d-430b-b762-84c75bd6a669%5C%22%3EPaul%20Semenza%2C%20professor%20and%20tech%20analyst%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Semanza%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20chair%20of%20the%20Engineering%20Management%20and%20Leadership%20Department%20at%20Santa%20Clara%20University%20and%20an%20analyst%20who%20focuses%20on%20tech%20hardware%2C%20said%20Apple%20is%20unlikely%20to%20settle%20this%20suit%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20an%20existing%20Apple%20employee%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20bringing%20parts%20to%20an%20interview%20seems%20more%20like%20a%20test%20of%20how%20desperate%20they%20are%20to%20work%20at%20OpenAI%20than%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%20%26quot%3BTargeting%20Apple's%20supply%20chain%20is%20a%20declaration%20of%20war.%20And%20given%20that%20Apple%20fought%20Samsung%20for%20years%20over%20rounded%20corners%2C%20it%20is%20hardly%20surprising%20to%20see%20Apple%20listing%20metal%20finishing%20as%20an%20example%20of%20IP%20theft.%20The%20question%20here%20is%20how%20this%20gets%20settled%2C%20given%20that%2C%20unlike%20with%20Samsung%2C%20Apple%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20cross-licensing%20anything%20from%20OpenAI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ff0ce3b-3681-40d2-917a-fa0ca5a779bb%5C%22%3EAlistair%20Barr%2C%20author%20of%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%2C%20the%20author%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20Big%20Tech%20newsletter%2C%20professed%20little%20sympathy%20for%20Apple%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCue%20the%20tiny%20violins%3B%20someone%20may%20have%20stolen%20something%20from%20Apple%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sorry%20tale%2C%20but%20one%20the%20tech%20giant%20knows%20very%20well.%20Maybe%20too%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarr%20goes%20on%20to%20detail%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-openai-trade-secrets-masimo-a123-jony-ive-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20filed%20against%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%2C%20Apple%20has%20itself%20faced%20lawsuits%20from%20companies%20accusing%20it%20of%20using%20remarkably%20similar%20tactics%3A%20recruiting%20away%20key%20employees%20and%20then%20using%20their%20knowledge%20to%20build%20competing%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227af827ed-ec5a-4256-899e-68bd2dbb8f31%5C%22%3ERohit%20Mittal%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Helium%20Ventures%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERohit%20Mittal%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Helium%20Ventures%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20acquires%20software%20businesses%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20not%20have%20Apple%20suing%20OpenAI%20on%20my%20bingo%20card%20for%20this%20year.%20They%20were%20the%20first%20to%20partner%20and%20integrate%20ChatGPT%20into%20their%20ecosystem.%20Crazy%20that%20Apple%20couldn't%20resolve%20this%20amicably%20and%20had%20to%20sue.%20Apple%20and%20Google%20have%20been%20partners%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20never%20heard%20about%20a%20lawsuit%20between%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2280ead0b2-c941-4a91-9cc4-1866c4e6d372%5C%22%3EParker%20Ortolani%2C%20product%20manager%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParker%20Ortolani%2C%20the%20associate%20director%20of%20product%20development%20at%20Penske%20Media%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3Bwell%20sun%20valley%20just%20got%20extra%20awkward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20past%20week%2C%20tech%20and%20media%20executives%20gathered%20in%20Sun%20Valley%20for%20the%20annual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsun-valley-fashion-sunglasses-shades-alex-karp-karlie-kloss-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAllen%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20invite-only%20gathering%20often%20called%20%26quot%3Bsummer%20camp%20for%20billionaires.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20is%20often%20a%20place%20for%20dealmaking%20behind%20closed%20doors.%20Apple's%20lawsuit%20became%20public%20just%20as%20the%20conference%20was%20ending%20and%20the%20executives%20began%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa4f8952-0999-43dd-b5b3-6ae0594fd301%5C%22%3EStephen%20Robles%2C%20podcaster%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Robles%2C%20the%20co-host%20of%20the%20Primary%20Tech%20podcast%2C%20responded%20on%20X%20to%20a%20post%20from%20Drew%20Pusateri%2C%20OpenAI's%20director%20of%20strategic%20communications%2C%20in%20which%20he%20shared%20the%20company's%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20other%20companies'%20trade%20secrets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobles%20pushed%20back%2C%20arguing%20that%20OpenAI's%20decision%20to%20hire%20Jony%20Ive%2C%20the%20famed%20iPhone%20designer%20whose%20company%20OpenAI%20also%20acquired%20and%20is%20named%20in%20Apple's%20suit%2C%20suggests%20an%20interest%20in%20Apple's%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'We%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20other%20companies'%20secrets%2C'%20while%20hiring%20Jony%20Ive%20to%20make%20you%20a%20device%20rings%20pretty%20hollow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIve%2C%20the%20designer%20behind%20many%20of%20Apple's%20most%20iconic%20products%2C%20left%20the%20company%20in%202019%20and%20later%20partnered%20with%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20to%20develop%20AI%20hardware.%20OpenAI%20acquired%20Ive's%20startup%2C%20io%2C%20in%202025%2C%20positioning%20Ive%20as%20a%20potential%20competitor%20to%20his%20former%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fd0ac45-f9c3-4c77-ba49-ab1efbabf229%5C%22%3EMax%20Weinbach%2C%20tech%20journalist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMax%20Weinbach%2C%20a%20tech%20journalist%20and%20analyst%20at%20Creative%20Strategies%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20focuses%20more%20on%20the%20alleged%20conduct%20of%20Chang%20Liu%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20electrical%20engineer%20at%20Apple%2C%20and%20Tang%20Tan%2C%20a%20former%20vice%20president%20at%20Apple%2C%20rather%20than%20on%20OpenAI%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20really%20seems%20like%20the%20suit%20is%20against%20Liu%20and%20Tan%20personally%20and%20OAI%20by%20extension%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BApple%20seems%20to%20really%20be%20pushing%20Liu%20and%20Tan%20as%20the%20bad%20actors%20and%20OAI%2C%20because%20it%20owns%20IO%2C%20rather%20than%20OAI%20was%20asking%20them%20to%20do%20all%20of%20this%20stuff.%20Nuance%2C%20but%20feels%20worth%20mentioning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d46ec8f-1e11-4fe0-a05e-6370a81fd5be%5C%22%3EPaul%20Lembo%2C%20tech%20executive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Lembo%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20Broadcom%2C%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20suing%20OpenAI%20for%20trade%20secret%20theft.%20Damn.%20Tim%20Cook%20is%20not%20Elon.%20He%20doesn't%20play.%20Knowing%20this%20was%20imminent%20was%20another%20reason%20for%20OpenAI%20not%20to%20IPO%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ex-employee%20theft%20angle%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20prove%20in%20court%2C%20but%20again%2C%20I%20expect%20Apple%20to%20bring%20heavy%20lumber%20to%20the%20bbq.%20We%20will%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22078724f0-c273-4d97-a730-abc1b862dbf2%5C%22%3ELivia%20Judith%20Szabo%2C%20venture%20capitalist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELivia%20Judith%20Szabo%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20executive%20chair%20of%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Moshulu%20Enterprise%20Partners%2C%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Apple%20vs.%20OpenAI%20lawsuit%20is%20a%20masterclass%20in%20partner-competitor%20risk%20for%20VCs%20and%20M%26amp%3BA%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20filing%20(July%2010%2C%202026)%20reads%20like%20a%20due%20diligence%20nightmare.%3Cbr%3ETrade%20secrets%2C%20400%2B%20poached%20engineers%2C%20and%20a%20hardware%20chief%20accused%20of%20coaching%20new%20hires%20on%20how%20to%20dodge%20exit%20security%20checks.%3Cbr%3ETwo%20once-close%20partners%2C%20now%20suing%20each%20other%20in%20federal%20court%2C%20weeks%20before%20OpenAI's%20expected%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lesson%20for%20founders%20raising%20serious%20capital%3A%20your%20IP%20and%20talent-transition%20protocols%20will%20get%20read%20line%20by%20line%20in%20diligence.%20Fix%20them%20before%20someone%20else's%20lawyers%20find%20them%20for%20you.%20This%20is%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20risk%20we%20flag%20before%20term%20sheets%20get%20signed%2C%20not%20after.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268054763-600c-4d32-b1df-a72a39a26ae9%5C%22%3EPeter%20Rojas%2C%20tech%20and%20media%20executive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Rojas%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20Mozilla%20leading%20new%20products%2C%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20how%20strong%20Apple's%20claims%20are%2C%20but%20I%20doubt%20they%20would%20be%20this%20aggressive%20if%20they%20weren't%20deeply%20concerned%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20planning%20on%20making%20a%20phone.%20I%20still%20think%20it's%20a%20better%20move%20for%20OpenAI%20than%20some%20sort%20of%20AI%20wearable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222accdc11-96d3-474d-99a7-e442a335cb74%5C%22%3ESahil%20Patel%2C%20marketing%20executive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESahil%20Patel%2C%20the%20social%20lead%20at%2