irways%2C%20but%20they%20have%20been%20such%20great%20sports.%20This%20has%20almost%20gone%20from%20a%20wager%20to%20being%20a%20collaboration%20between%20two%20airlines%20and%20what%20seems%20like%20the%20entire%20internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Myhre%20couldn't%20resist%20one%20more%20jab.%20%26quot%3BMay%20the%20best%20Norwegian%20team%20win!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhow-to-watch-norway-vs-england-world-cup-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEngland%20and%20Norway%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20face%20off%20at%20Hard%20Rock%20Stadium%20in%20Miami%20at%205%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20quarterfinal%20match%20will%20pit%20tournament%20standouts%20like%20Harry%20Kane%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ferling-haaland-fashion-style-big-business-hermes-nike-hair-tie-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EErling%20Haaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20each%20other.%20As%20of%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20platforms%20like%20DraftKings%2C%20Polymarket%2C%20and%20Kalshi%20are%20predicting%20England%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fengland-norway-world-cup-bet-british-airways-norwegian-air-shuttle-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783797079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a529304d9d92978fe6a66db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fengland-norway-world-cup-bet-british-airways-norwegian-air-shuttle-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Norwegian%20Air%20Shuttle%20made%20a%20cheeky%20bet%20with%20British%20Airways%20on%20Instagram%20ahead%20of%20England%20and%20Norway's%20match%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%