eteria%2C%20I%20kept%20returning.%20Every%20trip%20North%20visiting%20cousins%20was%20bittersweet%3B%20she%20loved%20them%20so%20much%20that%20I%20questioned%20starting%20a%20life%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8e33cc4-6408-473c-8a41-3a7b94ce7fb2%5C%22%3EI%20slowly%20found%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20flyer%20on%20the%20library's%20bulletin%20board%20introduced%20a%20Friday%20playgroup%2C%2040%20minutes%20away.%20Twelve%20moms%20awkwardly%20made%20small%20talk%20while%2030%20kids%20ran%20wild.%20Violet%20clung%20to%20me.%20When%20the%20playgroup%20ended%20two%20months%20later%2C%20we%20were%20just%20starting%20to%20warm%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20mom%20also%20wanted%20community%2C%20so%20she%20reached%20out.%20Our%20smaller%20group%20was%20less%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20very%20slowly%2C%20organically%20grew.%20The%20kids%20loved%20each%20other.%20We%20moms%20do%2C%20too%2C%20bonding%20over%20stories%20of%20new%20mom%20fears%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwas-never-good-making-friends-these-five-things-helped-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficulty%20of%20finding%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20six%20families%20with%2012%20kids%20meet%20four%20hours%20multiple%20times%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20more%20time%20than%20I've%20spent%20with%20anyone%20besides%20my%20husband%20since%20high-school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220fb9939c-5923-42bf-953c-49fe44e2d475%5C%22%3EMeeting%20other%20moms%20helped%20my%20mental%20health%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20Violet's%20birth%2C%20my%20husband%20became%20disabled%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-died-family-children-take-on-her-role-responsibilities-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emom%20died%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Suddenly%20transitioning%20careers%2C%20I%20also%20navigated%20the%20new%20terrain%20of%20motherhood%20and%20loss.%20Denial%20and%20newborn%20demands%20cushioned%20me%20from%20realizing%20how%20alone%20and%20frightened%20I%20felt.%20I%20reached%20for%20the%20phone%20to%20call%20my%20mother%20when%20Violet%20didn't%20latch%20immediately%2C%20or%20to%20ask%20for%20suggestions%20for%20safe%20bug%20spray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20jumped%20out%20of%20bed%20at%20midnight%20to%20trim%201-year-old%20Violet's%20tiny%20nails%2C%20convinced%20she'd%20scratch%20her%20eyes%2C%20then%20an%20hour%20later%20woke%20her%20again%20to%20change%20her%20bedding%2C%20sure%20she'd%20choke%20on%20a%20nail%20clipping%2C%20my%20husband%20gently%20suggested%20postpartum%20depression.%20I%20insisted%20he%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20a%20community%20of%20other%20moms%20brought%20joy%20and%20confidence%20back%20into%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I%20hadn't%20known%20I'd%20missed.%20They%20gave%20me%20a%20perspective%20no%20one%20else%20could%2C%20helping%20me%20relax%20and%20enjoy%20motherhood.%20Violet%20sang%20the%20names%20of%20her%20friends%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Another%20mom%20said%20her%20kids%20recite%20their%20friends'%20names%20in%20the%20car%2C%20and%20a%20third%20shared%20her%20girls%20say%20them%20alongside%20their%20bedtime%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20ice%20storm%20came.%20Our%20Middle%20Tennessee%20area%20was%20the%20hardest%20hit%2C%20stuck%20without%20power%20for%20six%20days.%20When%20my%20phone%20reconnected%20on%20the%20third%20day%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20chain%20of%20concerned%20texts%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Moms%26quot%3B%20(as%20my%20husband%20dubbed%20us).%20The%20family%20closest%20to%20us%20took%20us%20in%2C%20turning%20our%20disaster%20into%20a%20fun%20sleepover%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20relationships%20deepened%20as%20we%20shared%20how%20deeply%20we%20appreciated%20each%20other%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20for%20our%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%2C%20from%20a%20small%20library%20flyer%2C%20this%20mom%20group%20had%20now%20bettered%20all%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221789226-621a-414a-998e-9700185090f4%5C%22%3EWe%20support%20each%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20ages%20range%20from%2026%20to%2043%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20don't%20feel%20older.%20We're%20from%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20include%20a%20former%20engineer%20and%20a%20pandemic%20nurse.%20They%20all%20plan%20to%20homeschool%20their%20multiple%20children.%20I'm%20the%20only%20mom%20still%20working%2C%20and%20with%20just%20one%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unspoken%20motto%20in%20our%20group%20is%20that%20different%20families%20have%20different%20rules%2C%20and%20we%20support%20each%20other.%20Whenever%20new%20moms%20come%20to%20the%20library%2C%20we%20welcome%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20birthdays%20rolled%20around%2C%20Violet%20eagerly%20anticipated%20hers.%20When%20we%20asked%20what%20she%20wanted%2C%20she%20shouted%3A%20%26quot%3BAllllll%20my%20friends!%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-rural-tennessee-finding-mom-friends-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783792201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d749c360acd489560b742%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-rural-tennessee-finding-mom-friends-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20struggling%20to%20make%20friends%20for%20years%2C%20one%20library%20flyer%20led%20to%20the%20close-knit%20mom%20community%20we'd%20been%20searching%20for.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sari%20Caine)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft%20defends%20Asha%20Sharma%2C%20says%20she%20is%20an%20American%20CEO%20and%20Xbox%20layoff%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20H-1B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783792060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic