s.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat%2Farticleshow%2F132334422.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132334422.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPresident%20Trump%20threatened%20Iran%20with%20massive%20missile%20strikes%20if%20assassination%20plots%20are%20pursued.%20This%20warning%20dramatically%20escalated%20tensions%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20Disagreements%20over%20a%20maritime%20deal's%20interpretation%20fueled%20renewed%20military%20exchanges.%20Iran%20vowed%20revenge%20for%20past%20actions%20and%20perceived%20US%20treaty%20violations.%20Ambiguity%20and%20mistrust%20now%20threaten%20another%20fragile%20understanding%20between%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Chidanand%20Rajghatta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat%2Farticleshow%2F132334422.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat%2Famp_articleshow%2F132334422.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat%2Famp_articleshow%2F132334422.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Instagram's%20newest%20AI%20tool%20didn't%20survive%20the%20week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holds%20an%20iPhone%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a527041d9d92978fe6a66b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInstagram%20launched%20a%20new%20AI%20tool%20on%20Tuesday.%20It%20was%20gone%20by%20Friday.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Barclay%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20launched%20a%20new%20AI%20image%20generation%20model%2C%20Muse%20Image%2C%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tool%20allowed%20users%20to%20generate%20AI%20images%20based%20on%20public%20Instagram%20posts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFollowing%20backlash%20from%20users%20and%20entertainment%20groups%2C%20the%20feature%20is%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20as%20a%20routine%20product%20drop.%20Then%20it%20spiraled%20into%20a%20PR%20nightmare.%20Now%20it's%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Meta%20said%20a%20new%20feature%20that%20allowed%20users%20to%20generate%20AI%20images%20from%20public%20Instagram%20posts%20is%20no%20longer%20available.%20Users%20learned%20of%20the%20feature%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20Meta%20unveiled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-new-muse-image-ai-model-default-instagram-sharing-rules-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMuse%20Image%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20first%20image-generation%20model%20from%20Meta%20Superintelligence%20Labs.%20Muse%20Image%20is%20available%20through%20Meta%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20intent%20was%20to%20provide%20a%20useful%20creative%20tool%20and%20to%20give%20people%20control%20over%20whether%20their%20public%20content%20could%20be%20referenced%20in%20this%20way.%20We've%20heard%20the%20feedback%20that%20this%20feature%20missed%20the%20mark%2C%20so%20it's%20no%20longer%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Meta%20said%20in%20an%20Instagram%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta's%20Muse%20Image%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5269a2daf4d560957bfcbb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta%20announced%20the%20tool%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cp%3EInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Muse%20Image%20features%2C%20like%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20edits%20directly%20on%20photos%2C%20are%20still%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20users%20swiftly%20rebuked%20the%20feature%20after%20its%20rollout.%20They%20said%20it%20raised%20privacy%20concerns%20and%20created%20space%20for%20deepfake%20content.%20Many%20users%20shared%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20feature%20on%20social%20media%20sites%20like%20X%20and%20Reddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivacy%20advocates%20like%20Apar%20Gupta%2C%20the%20founding%20director%20of%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%2C%20criticized%20Meta%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20Meta%20owns%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20and%20we're%20forced%20to%20use%20it%2C%20it's%20been%20taking%20it%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20violate%20our%20consent%20and%20privacy%20again%20and%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Gupta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntertainment%20groups%20also%20criticized%20the%20feature.%20SAG-AFTRA%2C%20a%20labor%20union%20representing%20about%20160%2C000%20entertainment%20and%20media%20professionals%2C%20urged%20its%20members%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20SAG-AFTRA%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Banything%20other%20than%20a%20clear%20and%20conspicuous%20OPT-IN%20for%20these%20types%20of%20uses%20of%20Instagram%20users'%20images%20is%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20an%20utter%20miscalculation%20of%20public%20sentiment%20regarding%20the%20obvious%20dangers%20and%20harms%20inherent%20in%20such%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20applauded%20Meta's%20decision%20to%20reel%20back%20the%20feature.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20dangers%20of%20nonconsensual%20digital%20replicas%20well%20known%20to%20all%2C%20a%20feature%20that%20encouraged%20that%20behavior%20is%20unwise.%20We%20appreciate%20its%20discontinuance.%20It%20is%20the%20responsible%20thing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20union%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreative%20Artists%20Agency%2C%20a%20talent%20group%20representing%20a%20slew%20of%20A-list%20stars%2C%20also%20criticized%20the%20feature.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one's%20name%2C%20image%2C%20likeness%2C%20voice%2C%20or%20creative%20work%20should%20be%20used%20by%20any%20third%20party%2C%20including%20AI%20models%2C%20without%20clear%2C%20documented%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shared%20with%20Variety.%20%26quot%3BTrue%20innovation%20puts%20creators%20first%3A%20respecting%20their%20rights%2C%20protecting%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20giving%20them%20real%20control%2C%20not%20handing%20it%20over%20to%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20become%20a%20source%20of%20tension%20for%20entertainers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20worry%20that%20it%20will%20be%20used%20to%20steal%20their%20likeness%2C%20voices%2C%20or%20iconic%20phrases%20without%20their%20consent.%20Celebrities%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-celebrities-trademarks-protections-ai-taylor-swift-jimmy-kimmel-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMatthew%20McConaughey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jeremy%20Clarkson%20have%20registered%20trademarks%20to%20protect%20their%20likeness%20from%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Meta%2C%20OpenAI%20faced%20backlash%20after%20releasing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsora-openai-chatgpt-sam-altman-ai-shutting-down-farewell-why-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESora%202%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI%20video-generation%20platform%2C%20in%202025.%20The%20platform%20initially%20allowed%20users%20to%20create%20content%20featuring%20trademarked%20characters%2C%20drawing%20ire%20from%20entertainment%20companies%20such%20as%20Studio%20Ghibli.%20Although%20OpenAI%20secured%20a%20partnership%20with%20Disney%20to%20legally%20use%20those%20characters%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-discontinues-sora-video-app-amid