l%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20the%20marriage%20of%20Sen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20former%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Elaine%20Chao%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227489%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20his%20wife%20Elaine%20Chao.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5139e49d0a41df475c8a09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERepublican%20Sen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20former%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Elaine%20Chao.%3Cp%3ESHAWN%20THEW%2FPOOL%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERepublican%20Sen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20of%20Kentucky%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Elaine%20Chao%2C%20wed%20in%201993.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChao%20served%20as%20Transportation%20Secretary%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcConnell%2C%2084%2C%20has%20been%20hospitalized%20for%20nearly%204%20weeks%2C%20with%20few%20details%20available%20about%20his%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERepublican%20Sen.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaga-trump-senate-majority-leader-race-rick-scott-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMitch%20McConnell%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20hospitalized%20for%20nearly%20four%20weeks%2C%20with%20few%20details%20available%20about%20his%20health%2C%20prompting%20growing%20questions%20about%20his%20condition%20and%20what%20members%20of%20his%20inner%20circle%2C%20including%20his%20wife%2C%20Elaine%20Chao%2C%20have%20been%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell%20and%20Chao%20met%20through%20a%20mutual%20friend%20and%20wed%20in%20a%20private%20Capitol%20ceremony%20in%201993%2C%20and%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-wife-usha-vance-relationship-trump-politics-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGOP%20power%20couple%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell%20has%20served%20as%20a%20US%20senator%20for%20over%2040%20years.%20Chao%20made%20history%20as%20the%20first%20Asian%20American%20woman%20to%20serve%20in%20a%20presidential%20Cabinet%20after%20she%20was%20confirmed%20as%20secretary%20of%20labor%20in%202001%2C%20during%20George%20W.%20Bush's%20administration.%20In%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20Chao%20was%20appointed%20transportation%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell's%20Senate%20office%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%20their%20relationship%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMitch%20McConnell%2C%2084%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20longest-serving%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20Senate.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22988%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20speaks%20at%20an%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F596fb8c2c50c2935008b549e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22741%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitch%20McConnell.%3Cp%3EMark%20Wilson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20grew%20up%20in%20Alabama%20and%20Kentucky%20and%20became%20a%20US%20senator%20representing%20Kentucky%20in%201985.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20both%20the%20Senate%20minority%20leader%20and%20the%20Senate%20majority%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20serving%20his%20final%20term%20and%20is%20not%20seeking%20reelection%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EElaine%20Chao%2C%2073%2C%20served%20as%20the%20US%20secretary%20of%20transportation%20during%20President%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elaine%20Chao%20speaks%20in%20Congress%2C%20with%20Mitch%20McConnell%20visible%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5890dad7713ba157008b5b94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElaine%20Chao.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FCarlos%20Barria%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChao%20was%20the%20first%20Asian-American%20woman%20to%20be%20appointed%20to%20a%20presidential%20cabinet.%20She%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20US%20secretary%20of%20labor%20from%202001%20to%202009%2C%20under%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Taiwan%20at%20age%208%20and%20grew%20up%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcConnell%20and%20Chao%20met%20through%20a%20mutual%20friend%2C%20Stuart%20Bloch%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223159%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5127519d0a41df475c88ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitch%20McConnell%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3Cp%3ELaura%20Patterson%2FCQ%20Roll%20Call%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBloch%20and%20McConnell%20met%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2014%2F05%2F14%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fgirding-for-a-fight-mcconnell-enlists-his-wife.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Bloch%20was%20married%20to%20Julia%20Chang%20Bloch%2C%20who%20was%20a%20mentor%20of%20Chao's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloch%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20he%20invited%20McConnell%20to%20a%20candlelit%20dinner%20with%20Chao.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20that%20sparks%20flew%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloch%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20that's%20not%20the%20way%20either%20of%20them%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloch%20also%20described%20Chao%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btiger%20wife%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bmade%20of%20titanium.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20married%20on%20February%206%2C%201993%2C%20in%20a%20private%20ceremony%20in%20the%20chapel%20of%20the%20US%20Capitol.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20Elaine%20Chao%20pose%20before%20their%20marriage%20in%20the%20chapel%20of%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%20February%206%2C%201993.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aae9420fe7c5222008b494f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22858%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20(R-Ky.)%2C%20poses%20with%20Elaine%20L.%20Chao%2C%20president%20of%20United%20Way%20of%20America%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20in%20Washington%2C%20Feb.%206%2C%201993%2C%20before%20their%20marriage%20in%20the%20Chapel%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Capitol.%20The%20wedding%20was%20a%20private%20ceremony%20attended%20by%20their%20families.%3Cp%3EShayna%20Brennan%2FAP%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20chose%20that%20wedding%20date%20for%20three%20reasons%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Farchive%2Flifestyle%2F1998%2F02%2F04%2Fthe-reliable-source%2F1317d9ee-cb2b-4304-a3de-18f4dfc2cd3d%2F%3Futm_term%3D.4e057e4836cd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%3A%20It's%20Ronald%20Reagan's%20birthday%2C%20it%20was%20just%20before%20Chao's%2040th%20birthday%2C%20and%20it%20was%20right%20before%20a%20one-week%20Senate%20recess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcConnell%20was%20previously%20married%20and%20has%20three%20children%20from%20that%20relationship.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20Elaine%20Chao%20holding%20hands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aae971292c06933008b4954%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitch%20McConnell%20and%20Elaine%20Chao%20holding%20hands.%3Cp%3EPablo%20Alcala%2FAP%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell's%20first%20wife%2C%20Sherrill%20Redmon%2C%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20feminist%20scholar.%20The%20two%20divorced%20in%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%201998%2C%20the%20couple%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%20how%20they%20divide%20household%20labor.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elaine%20chao%20mitch%20mconnell%20hugging%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aae9773b085c029008b4877%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22975%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%2C%20R-Ky.%2C%20greets%20his%20wife%2C%20Labor%20Secretary%20Elaine%20Chao%2C%20after%20introducing%20her%20at%20the%20Republican%20National%20Convention%20Wednesday%2C%20Sept.1%2C%202004%2C%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EJ.%20SCOTT%20APPLEWHITE%2FAP%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell%20cooked%20once%20in%20a%20while%20and%20did%20the%20laundry%2C%20while%20Chao%20was%20responsible%20for%20fixing%20things%20around%20the%20house%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChao%20has%20often%20campaigned%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20becoming%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcampaign%20hugger%2C%26quot%3B%20Time%20magazine%20reported.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20wife%20Elaine%20Chao%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20in%202008%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63767cd41f38cc0012879080%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22663%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFLORENCE%2C%20KY%20-%20OCTOBER%2031%3A%20U.S.%20Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Sen.%20Mitch%20McConnell%20(R-KY)%20(C)%20and%20his%20wife%20U.%20S.%20Secretary%20of%20Labor%20Elaine%20Chao%20wave%20to%20supporters%20during%20a%20campaign%20stop%20on%20October%2031%2C%202008%20in%20Florence%2C%20Kentucky.%20McConnell%20is%20seeking%20re-election%20in%20a%20tight%20race%20with%20challenger%20former%20Kentucky%20Democratic%20Party%20treasurer%20Bruce%20Lunsford.%3Cp%3EMark%20Lyons%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcConnell%20had%20polio%20as%20a%20child%20and%20finds%20backslapping%20painful%2C%20so%20Chao%20has%20stepped%20in%20to%20hug%20constituents%20in%20his%20stead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20very%20actively%20listens.%20She%20really%20pays%20attention%20and%20remembers%20details%20about%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Kelly%20Westwood%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Kenton%20County%20women's%20Republican%20group%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F3574652%2Fmitch-mcconnells-secret-weapon-his-wife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETime%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014.%20%26quot%3BShe%20doesn't%20see%20them%20for%20months%20and%20then%20says%2C%20'I%20know%20you%20sprained%20your%20arm%2C%20how's%20it%20going%3F'%20Or%2C%20'How's%20%5Byour%5D%20bid%20for%20city%20council%20going%3F'%20She%20remembers%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%20has%20also%20starred%20in%20campaign%20ads%20defending%20McConnell's%20record%20on%20women's%20issues.%20In%20a%202014%20campaign%20ad%2C%20she%20praised%20McConnell%20as%20a%20co-sponsor%20of%20the%20original%20Violence%20Against%20Women%20Act%20in%201991%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftalkingpointsmemo.com%2Fdc%2Fmitch-mcconnell-ad-vawa-elaine-chao%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETalking%20Points%20Memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointed%20out%2C%20McConnell%20voted%20against%20the%20final%20legislation%20in%201993%20and%20its%20reauthorizations%20in%202012%20and%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202017%2C%20when%20Trump%20criticized%20McConnell%20on%20X%2C%20Chao%20responded%20by%20telling%20reporters%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20stand%20by%20my%20man%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elaine%20chao%20donald%20trump%20Charlottesville%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ab005c5873dc6a0118b4a7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETransportation%20Secretary%20Elaine%20Chao%20looks%20on%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20following%20a%20meeting%20on%20infrastructure%20at%20Trump%20Tower%2C%20August%2015%2C%202017%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20He%20fielded%20questions%20from%20reporters%20about%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20events%20in%20Charlottesville%2C%20Virginia%20and%20white%20supremacists.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20McConnell%20said%20the%20White%20House%20had%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%20expectations%26quot%3B%20for%20Congress%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Kentucky%20in%20August%202017%2C%20Trump%20took%20to%20X%2C%20then%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSenator%20Mitch%20McConnell%20said%20I%20had%20'excessive%20expectations%2C'%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20so.%20After%207%20years%20of%20hearing%20Repeal%20%26amp%3B%20Replace%2C%20why%20not%20done%3F%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20posted%20again%20the%20following%20day%3A%20%26quot%3BMitch%2C%20get%20back%20to%20work%20and%20put%20Repeal%20%26amp%3B%20Replace%2C%20Tax%20Reform%20%26amp%3B%20Cuts%20and%20a%20great%20Infrastructure%20Bill%20on%20my%20desk%20for%20signing.%20You%20can%20do%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReporters%20asked%20Chao%2C%20who%20had%20attended%20an%20infrastructure%20meeting%20at%20Trump%20Tower%2C%20what%20she%20thought%20of%20Trump's%20comments.%20She%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20stand%20by%20my%20man%20%E2%80%94%20both%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20reported%20that%20McConnell's%20wealth%20had%20increased%20sevenfold%20in%2010%20years%2C%20from%20%243.1%20million%20in%202004%20to%20%2422.8%20million%20in%202014.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elaine%20chao%20mitch%20mconnell%2014%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5aae94f189188d2d0