20entertainment%2C%20and%20taxes%20were%20all%20much%20higher%20than%20I%20had%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pedestrians%20walk%20past%20pastel%20historic%20storefronts%20on%20a%20sunny%20street%20with%20palm%20trees%20and%20shop%20awnings.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8c0cd3a449ec3445f587%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20historic%20downtown%20of%20Charleston%2C%20South%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Greenberg%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southern%20charm%20I%20was%20hoping%20for%20also%20didn't%20feel%20as%20I%20expected.%20Charleston%20has%20a%20big%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20out%26quot%3B%20culture%2C%20much%20of%20which%20seems%20to%20revolve%20around%20where%20to%20eat%20or%20drink.%20That's%20not%20really%20my%20thing.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20city%20lacked%20some%20of%20the%20creative%20flavor%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20climate%20was%20another%20big%20factor.%20Everyone%20knows%20New%20England%20can%20have%20brutal%20winters%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20like%20shoveling%20snow%2C%20so%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20get%20away%20from%20that.%20But%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwealthy-leaving-california-new-york-moving-florida-texas-reasons-effects-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20South%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20traded%20brutal%20winters%20for%20brutal%20summers.%20It%20was%20just%20so%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20just%20needed%20time%20to%20adjust.%20But%20the%20more%20I%20explored%20Charleston%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realized%20the%20lifestyle%20I%20had%20imagined%20didn't%20match%20my%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20getting%20annoyed%2C%20then%20frustrated%2C%20and%20then%20I%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278ce1320-36b2-4cbd-9a7a-6be6b11070f9%5C%22%3EI%20tried%20the%20South%20again%2C%20but%20it%20still%20wasn't%20for%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20had%20anything%20to%20lose%2C%20so%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20Connecticut%20in%202022.%20Instead%20of%20feeling%20defeated%2C%20I%20actually%20felt%20grateful%20that%20I%20had%20given%20Charleston%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20rented%20a%20month-to-month%20beach%20house%20in%20Connecticut%20while%20I%20looked%20for%20a%20home%20to%20buy.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-housing-markets-highest-demand-competition-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehomebuying%20search%20in%20New%20England%20felt%20bleak%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20downsize%2C%20but%20even%20the%20smaller%20homes%20came%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarter-homes-prices-expensive-cost-1-million-us-cities-zillow-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewith%20big-home%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20might%20never%20find%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20house%20hunting%20for%2014%20months%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20put%20down%20roots.%20The%20idea%20of%20moving%20to%20a%20quieter%2C%20more%20affordable%20small%20town%20was%20still%20appealing.%20So%20in%20July%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20the%20South%20again%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20in%20Beaufort%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20a%20small%20town%20I%20had%20explored%20while%20living%20in%20Charleston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20purchase%20a%20beautiful%20three-bedroom%20ranch%20home%20for%20%24425%2C000.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20build%20in%20a%20planned%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20checked%20a%20lot%20of%20boxes.%20It%20was%20beautiful%2C%20new%2C%20and%20far%20more%20affordable%20than%20what%20I%20could%20have%20bought%20in%20Connecticut.%20But%20I%20still%20didn't%20feel%20at%20home%20in%20Beaufort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2d75505-3b70-4cd2-833f-7c7c91f26d50%5C%22%3EAffordability%20is%20important%2C%20but%20you%20also%20need%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Beaufort%2C%20it%20was%20so%20hot%20that%20I%20rarely%20saw%20or%20interacted%20with%20my%20neighbors.%20People%20would%20say%20hello%20and%20then%20quickly%20go%20back%20inside.%20I%20kept%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20am%20I%20ever%20going%20to%20socialize%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joke%20that%20I'm%20an%20OG%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-ai-entry-level-hiring-new-grads-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20started%20working%20remotely%20in%202008.%20Remote%20work%20gives%20you%20some%20social%20interaction%2C%20but%20you%20still%20need%20to%20get%20outside%20and%20make%20real%20connections%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20to%20put%20myself%20in%20situations%20where%20I%20could%20meet%20people.%20I%20looked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoing-yoga-every-day-5-years-changed-womans-body-diet-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor%20yoga%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20local%20events%2C%20and%20other%20activities%20I%20could%20join.%20But%20what%20I%20found%20was%20that%20many%20people%20had%20moved%20there%20for%20family%20or%20moved%20with%20a%20spouse%2C%20and%20they%20mostly%20kept%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20lacked%20the%20kind%20of%20community%20connection%20I%20was%20used%20to%20seeing%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20I%20kept%20trying%20to%20make%20those%20connections%20and%20stay%20open%20to%20it%2C%20but%20it%20just%20kept%20falling%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20people%20this%20story%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20understand%20it%2C%20and%20sometimes%20they%20don't.%20But%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20done%20one%20morning%20when%20I%20woke%20up%2C%20looked%20at%20the%20ceiling%20fan%20in%20my%20bedroom%2C%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20hate%20that%20fan%2C%20and%20I'm%20losing%20hope%20for%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1dc8d8d-8d8e-4c98-a64b-c97d1b7714cf%5C%22%3EI%20didn't%20appreciate%20Connecticut's%20beauty%20until%20I%20moved%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20I%20moved%20back%20to%20Connecticut.%20Right%20now%2C%20I'm%20living%20on%20the%20coast%20in%20an%20apartment%20inside%20a%20refurbished%20Civil%20War-era%20hospital.%20I'm%20on%20one%20of%20the%20top%20floors%2C%20so%20I%20can%20see%20the%20boats%20and%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20searching%20for%20a%20home%20and%20making%20offers%20with%20more%20confidence.%20Home%20prices%20are%20high%20here%2C%20but%20prices%20down%20South%20are%20creeping%20up%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20started%20thinking%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-to-connecticut-job-work-hartford-benefits-surprisingly-great-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eowning%20in%20Connecticut%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20as%20an%20investment%20in%20both%20my%20future%20and%20my%20happiness.%20I've%20set%20a%20budget%20of%20about%20%24800%2C000%20for%20a%20home%2C%20though%20some%20of%20the%20homes%20I've%20been%20interested%20in%20have%20been%20closer%20to%20%24650%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20seeing%20possibilities%20I%20didn't%20see%20before%2C%20and%20that's%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandy%20shoreline%20curves%20along%20a%20calm%20bay%20with%20small%20boats%2C%20coastal%20houses%2C%20yellow%20flowers%2C%20and%20distant%20islands.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8c92d3b3e45765196a13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sandy%20bay%20in%20Connecticut.%3Cp%3EKate%20Stoupas%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20back%20in%20Connecticut%20has%20been%20eye-opening.%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20fully%20appreciated%20its%20beauty%20until%20I%20had%20something%20to%20compare%20it%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20so%20much%20opportunity%20here.%20I%20love%20the%20energy%20and%20the%20people.%20I've%20been%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20location%2C%20too%2C%20doing%20things%20like%20hopping%20on%20a%20train%20to%20New%20York%20to%20see%20a%20show%20or%20making%20more%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20connect%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20think%20about%20whether%20I'd%20move%20somewhere%20else%20again%2C%20I%20keep%20coming%20back%20to%20something%20a%20photographer%20once%20told%20me%20in%20Massachusetts.%20He%20had%20lived%20in%20Bali%20with%20his%20family%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20asking%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20lived%20in%20Bali%3F%20Why%20would%20you%20come%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-massachusetts-has-the-best-economy-in-the-us-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20Massachusetts%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20never%20forget%20what%20he%20told%20me.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20go%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20from%20an%20airport%2C%20but%20you%20really%20have%20to%20realize%20the%20ground%20beneath%20your%20feet%20is%20beautiful%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20see%20it%20that%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20stayed%20with%20me.%20It%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20think%20about%20Connecticut%20and%20made%20me%20realize%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20the%20blinders%20off.%20There%20was%20beauty%20right%20at%20my%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20needed%20to%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-connecticut-to-south-carolina-disliked-heat-crowds-traffic-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783775641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4e8ef4d3b3e45765196a2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-connecticut-to-south-carolina-disliked-heat-c