tigenerational-homes-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20of%20communal%20living%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20flexibility.%20I'm%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20a%20season%20of%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I'm%20open%20to%20whatever%20living%20scenarios%20the%20future%20may%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20wish%20I%20lived%20in%20an%20area%20that's%20within%20walking%20distance%20to%20coffee%20shops%2C%20libraries%2C%20artistic%20experiences%2C%20and%20friends.%20But%20I%20made%20this%20decision%20to%20live%20so%20close%20to%20my%20parents%20based%20on%20what%20I%20felt%20I%20needed%20at%20the%20time.%20It's%20been%20helpful%2C%20meaningful%2C%20and%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20during%20a%20tough%2C%20busy%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20what%20the%20future%20of%20being%20neighbors%20with%20my%20parents%20will%20bring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flived-with-parents-adult-now-neighbors-benefits-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783771621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d326894175b768171fb18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flived-with-parents-adult-now-neighbors-benefits-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20lived%20with%20my%20parents%20for%20six%20years.%20When%20they%20wanted%20to%20downsize%2C%20I%20moved%20into%20a%20townhouse%20across%20the%20street.%20Being%20their%20neighbor%20is%20fun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Samantha%20Paige%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20colleague%20wanted%20a%20nerdy%2C%20niche%20tool%20for%20his%20MacBook.%20Codex%20whipped%20it%20up%20in%20minutes.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22