ssinsider.com%2Fopenai-codex-chatgpt-app-releases-gpt-5-6-models-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECodex%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20made%20it%20better.%20I've%20long%20wanted%20a%20version%20of%20copy-paste%20that%20lets%20me%20store%20multiple%20strings%20of%20text%20at%20once%2C%20so%20I%20can%20copy%20something%20new%20without%20losing%20what%20I'd%20copied%20before.%20There%20are%20clipboard%20managers%20for%20this%20online%2C%20but%20they%20often%20cost%20money%2C%20or%20add%20a%20pop-up%20and%20additional%20clicks%20%E2%80%94%20exactly%20the%20slowdowns%20I%20don't%20want.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI%20gave%20OpenAI's%20tool%20a%20190-word%20prompt%2C%20and%20voila!%20Five%20minutes%20and%2026%20seconds%20later%2C%20Codex%20handed%20me%20my%20app.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENow%2C%20I%20have%209%20different%20copy-paste%20slots%20on%20my%20work%20MacBook.%20Command-c%20and%20command-v%20work%20as%20normal%2C%20that's%20slot%20one.%20But%20now%20I%20can%20keep%20additional%20names%2C%20quotes%2C%20and%20links%20at%20the%20tip%20of%20my%20tongue%3A%20cmd-c-2%20copies%20text%20for%20cmd-v-2%2C%20cmd-c-3%20ties%20to%20cmd-v-3%2C%20and%20on%20and%20on.%20The%20app%20hangs%20out%20on%20my%20menu%20bar%2C%20so%20if%20I%20want%20to%20see%20what%20each%20slot%20is%20storing%2C%20it's%20all%20a%20click%20away.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVery%20satisfying.%20It's%20exactly%20the%20niche%20and%20nerdy%20case%20that%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuild-app-no-coding-skills-ai-lovable-replit-claude%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Evibe%20coding%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20good%20for.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3