om%2Fgetting-divorced-advice-attorney-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivorce%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20otherwise.%20I%20am%20still%20pushing%20on%20from%20that%20deficit%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20work%20nearly%20four%20to%20five%20times%20as%20hard%20just%20to%20keep%20everything%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20my%20Hamptons%20rent%20is%20a%20struggle.%20I%20pay%20around%20%244%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20including%20utilities%2C%20basic%20maintenance%2C%20and%20house%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20cost%20of%20renting%20a%20home%20here%20doesn't%20stop%20at%20rent.%20Lawn%20care%2C%20air%20conditioning%2C%20pool%20maintenance%2C%20and%20basic%20upkeep%20add%20up%20quickly.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-22000-month-renting-backyard-pools-los-angeles-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPool%20maintenance%3C%2Fa%3E%20alone%20can%20cost%20%243%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20or%20more.%20I%20remember%20this%20from%20when%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20took%20care%20of%20his%20family's%20property%2C%20and%20we%20were%20not%20even%20paying%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20pool%20maintenance%20during%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20I%20currently%20pay%20about%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20combined%20for%20air%20conditioning%20maintenance%20and%20pool%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245f198ae-61b7-4e36-bc62-395fb59d38ab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFeeding%20my%20family%20can%20get%20difficult%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGroceries%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20are%20extraordinarily%20overpriced.%20I%20am%20not%20even%20talking%20about%20some%20of%20the%20specialty%20markets%20like%20the%20famous%20Round%20Swamp%20Farm%20in%20East%20Hampton%20or%20Loaves%20%26amp%3B%20Fishes%2C%20where%20two%20items%20can%20easily%20be%20%2440.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%2C%20Lidl%2C%20and%20Walmart%20runs%20are%20necessary%20for%20my%20family.%20Most%20of%20my%20necessary%20shopping%20is%20in%20Riverhead%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhamptons-rush-staffing-summer-homes-nannies-chefs-estate-managers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHampton%20Bays%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20cheaper%20grocery%20stores%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20kids'%20lunches%2C%20I%20team%20up%20with%20a%20few%20other%20moms%20and%20pay%20one%20of%20them%20to%20make%20food%20for%20my%20kids%20for%20the%20week.%20I%20am%20so%20busy%20running%20around%20for%20my%20job%20that%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20constantly%20either%20driving%2C%20stuck%20in%20traffic%2C%20on%20my%20computer%20drafting%20emails%2C%20or%20reviewing%20contracts.%20Having%20that%20help%20with%20lunches%20is%20one%20less%20thing%20I%20have%20to%20worry%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224fffbaa4-547d-4788-9804-601a46535910%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20have%20also%20had%20to%20rethink%20my%20children's%20activities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20cut%20out%20private%20tennis%20lessons%20and%20instead%20enlisted%20buddies%20who%20are%20more%20senior%20players%20to%20play%20with%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20organizes%20soccer%20sessions%20at%20the%20park%2C%20even%20with%20children%20he%20has%20just%20met.%20I%20love%20seeing%20that%20because%20they%20are%20learning%20how%20to%20stay%20active%20and%20create%20their%20own%20fun%20without%20every%20activity%20having%20to%20come%20with%20a%20major%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20also%20become%20savvy%20with%20checking%20out%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-entrepreneurs-use-library-for-free-resources-to-get-ahead-2020-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20libraries%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Hamptons.%20Each%20one%20is%20different.%20I%20take%20my%20children%20there%20to%20participate%20in%20summer%20reading%20challenges%20and%20other%20programs.%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%20affordable%20classes%20and%20community%20offerings%2C%20like%20Italian%20in%20Bridgehampton%20and%20t'ai%20chi%20in%20Hampton%20Bays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20not%20allow%20my%20kids%20to%20go%20to%20the%20toy%20store%20or%20Dylan's%20Candy%20Bar%20as%20liberally%20as%20I%20once%20did.%20I%20tell%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20is%20not%20in%20your%20piggy%20bank%2C%20you%20cannot%20afford%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20has%20made%20homemade%20slime%2C%20lemonade%2C%20and%20iced%20tea%20to%20sell%20in%20our%20neighborhood%20so%20she%20and%20her%20brother%20can%20make%20extra%20cash%20to%20buy%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cbe920f-ad94-41b2-ba21-8ce18f6e8bae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20social%20life%20is%20a%20financial%20struggle%2C%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20purchase%20alcohol.%20Going%20out%20to%20eat%20for%20a%20party%20of%20four%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20can%20easily%20be%20well%20over%20%241%2C000%20if%20everyone%20has%20dinner%20and%20two%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20become%20savvy%20with%20learning%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-avoid-doing-work-happy-hour-etiquette-expert-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehappy%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20have%20no%20shame%20in%20asking%20whether%20a%20local's%20rate%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20also%20grateful%20for%20complimentary%20fitness%20classes%20around%20the%20Hamptons%2C%20typically%20sponsored%20by%20a%20brand.%20There%20are%20still%20ways%20to%20participate%20without%20spending%20a%20fortune%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20know%20where%20to%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22243701ec-1279-45f4-bba8-98d5e27d6f90%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20year-round%20means%20seeing%20both%20sides%20of%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20the%20glamorous%20version%20people%20come%20here%20for%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20and%20then%20there%20is%20the%20reality%20for%20locals%2C%20single%20parents%2C%20and%20small%20business%20owners%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20all%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20where%20I%20live%20and%20where%20I%20grew%20up.%20But%20summer%20here%20is%20not%20always%20easy%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20takes%20discipline%2C%20creativity%2C%20help%20from%20friends%2C%20and%20a%20constant%20willingness%20to%20adapt%20and%20be%20humble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-living-hamptons-struggling-financially-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783770421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a46953965e65d39ff1c9095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-living-hamptons-struggling-financially-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Raising%20my%20kids%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20is%20financially%20difficult.%20I%20have%20to%20travel%20out%20of%20town%20to%20grocery%20shop%2C%20and%20have%20to%20cut%20my%20kid's%20expensive%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Vanessa%20Gordon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20escaped%20Spanish%20wildfire%2C%20but%20our%20friends%20lost%20their%20lives'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1783770355000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F05e1%2Flive%2F765560f0-7d18-11f1-bee8-53ce494e1abc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc07y357zvl1o%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20firefighters%20in%20Spain%20have%20been%20battling%20a%20deadly%20wildfire%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc07y357zvl1o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20Birla%20Gr