%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496964%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20sure%20if%20football%20was%20her%20game.%20But%20when%20the%20coach%20handed%20her%20a%20ball%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20kick%20it%20away%20from%20yourself%20and%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%20something%20changed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20later%2C%20football%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20sport%20for%20Yamini%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ground%20has%20become%20her%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20home%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20rule%20that%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYamini%20studies%20in%20a%20government%20school%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20has%20always%20enjoyed%20going%20to%20class.%20Yet%20her%20idea%20of%20education%20changed%20when%20she%20joined%20the%20OSCAR%20Foundation.%20Its%20strict%20rule%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CNo%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20taught%20her%20that%20passion%20and%20discipline%20must%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-2_11zon-1757076501.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%